fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 added 195.40 points or 1.08% to settle at 18,264.40. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, advanced 2.76% to 12.64. HDFC Bank, Canara Bank, ICICI Bank were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The May 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 25 May 2023.
